        What to Expect When Selling in Hemmant
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Hemmant is a large-block eastern suburb that appeals to buyers seeking space, quiet streets and a bayside-fringe lifestyle at a price point that remains accessible relative to its inner-east neighbours.
      </p>
